OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Flargely dry and cloudy night with some
OL,7,Fclear intervals possible. A few spots
OL,8,Fof light rain are also possible.
OL,9,FModerate southerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy day with some
OL,12,Fbright or sunny intervals breaking
OL,13,Fthrough. Largely dry but a few
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain possible through the
OL,15,Fday. Moderate to fresh southerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
