OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCloudy
OL,6,FTuesday with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Finterspersed with dry and bright
OL,8,Fspells. Winds strengthening Wednesday
OL,9,Fas heavier rain spreads east, clearing
OL,10,Fto showers. Mostly cloudy with rain or
OL,11,Fshowers Thursday.
